Package co.cask.cdap.api

Interfaces for program and resource specifications, program lifecycle, runtime context and processors.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Predicate<T>
    Determines a true or false value for a given input.
    Processor
    Process with a Processor.
    ProgramLifecycle<T extends RuntimeContext>
    Defines program lifecycle.
    ProgramSpecification
    This interface provides for getting the name, class name, and description specifications of any type of program.
    RuntimeContext
    This interface represents a context for a processor or elements of a processor.
    ServiceDiscoverer
    An interface for Discovery Service.
    TxRunnable
    A runnable that provides a DatasetContext to programs which may be used to get access to and use datasets.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Resources
    Carries system resources requirements.
    SingleRunnableApplication
    A simple TwillApplication that contains only one TwillRunnable.
